<div class='media__message'>
<h4 class='h12 talk-link__speaker'>노니 델라 페냐(Nonny de la Peña)</h4>
<h4 class='h9 m5'>
<a class='' href='///home/acornjello/gitRepository/mirror/www.ted.com/talks/nonny_de_la_pena_the_future_of_news_virtual_reality?language=ko' lang='ko'>
뉴스의 미래요? 가상현실에 있습니다
</a>
</h4>
<div class='meta'>
<span class='meta__item'>
Posted
<span class='meta__val'>
Nov 2015
</span>
</span>
<span class='meta__row'>
Rated
<span class='meta__val'>
Informative, Fascinating
</span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

